Patch Set 11:

Hey,

I'm really sorry for this but I just realized that this test you're adding is already covered by the test right above of it (test_required_creds). Am i missing your point?

If my assumption is right, this patch doesn't seem to be needed.

Sorry for not catching this earlier.

Patch Set 11: I would prefer that you didn't merge this

above comment

Patch Set 11:

Hey :)
Sorry, can not agree with you. Previous test with the case with missing tenant raise exception before on step (https://github.com/openstack/glance/blob/master/glance/common/auth.py#L89) because auth. strategy is missed in the  cred dictionary.
So my test verifies raise of exception on step (https://github.com/openstack/glance/blob/master/glance/common/auth.py#L95)
May be we can change previous test by adding strategy value to the cred dictionary(for case with missed tenant) - in such case it will be duplicated checks.

Patch Set 11:

Right, I missed that part. So yes, pls, add another dict in the previous test and fix the comment in the one saying: "# v2.0: missing tenant"

Thank you very much and sorry for not noticing this before!

Cheers
